FBIS4-38082 "drnes124_p_94004" FBIS-NES-94-124 Daily Report 26 Jun 1994 SOUTH ASIA Afghanistan Government Seen Making Progress Against Militia Government Seen Making Progress Against Militia Opposition Attack `Foiled' LD2606191894 Kabul Radio Afghanistan Network in Pashto 1530 GMT 26 Jun 94 LD2606191894 Kabul Radio Afghanistan Network Pashto BFN [Text] An attack by Dostam-Golboddin's militia was foiled today in Samangan Province. According to a report sent to the Bakhtar Information Agency by Commander Hamidullah Tabashi, at around 0600 hours today Dostam-Golboddin's militia resorted to attacking the positions of forces of the Islamic Army and Mojahedin in the regions of Yalghar, Hazhdarai, and Dunyadara. As a result of a positive defense by Mojahedin and and Islamic Army forces, their attack faced a complete defeat. In the course of a reciprocal attack by the Mojahedin, two militia armored tanks were set ablaze and a large number militia were killed or injured.
